   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(Recto);;Ag[- - -], Phanotheos (and) Peton to Zenon greeting. We have [sent you] a copy of the petition sent to us from Theon, [which] Onnophris [presented] against Neoptolemos. Deliver the indictment(?) then to Neoptolemos [and] send him to us in order that he may be tried on the charge of his accuser [- - -]. If he fails to appear, we will pronounce judgment against him in favour of [the petitioner's claims(?)]. And also write to us. Farewell. Year 32, Daisios [. . .].;;(Verso);To Zenon.;(Docket, 2nd hand) Year 32, Epeiph 20. Against Neoptolemos.</ab>
         </div>
